data.description: This home is being offered by MOTIVATED SELLERS who are ready to make a deal. Bring your offers and let’s negotiate a win-win for everyone! Schedule a showing today and experience the perfect blend of luxury, comfort and natural beauty at this exceptional 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath + an office in Amelia Walk. As you enter you'll be captivated by the spacious living area that flows into the kitchen & dining. Kitchen boasts 2022 Samsung Bespoke appliances, granite counters, tile backsplash, pendant lights & a walk-in pantry. Owners suite overlooks the pond with attached ensuite bath complete with a walk-in shower & double vanities. Vinyl plank floors & 8-foot doors throughout. The brick paver drive adds elegance to the exterior + the front porch & extended screened lanai. Enjoy the zero-entry pool, stay active in the fitness room or host at the owner's clubhouse. Minutes away from the charming dt Fernandina Beach, shopping, restaurants & the shores of Amelia Island.
